    "en": "ROLE OF METHIONINE TRANSPORTER FUNCTION IN SULFUR PARTITIONING AND SOURCE-SINK PHYSIOLOGY OF NODULATED PEA (Pisum sativum L.) PLANTS",
    "ja": null,
